"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-refugee-olympic-team-2024-athletes-b1155246.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport  Today, theInternational Olympic Committee(IOC) revealed theathleteswho will represent the Refugee Olympic Team atthis year's Games.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999995401882336, \"rank\": 4.5981206997808623e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A cohort of 36 elite athletes, who are alsorefugees, will head to theOlympic GamesinParislater this year, competing for gold across 12 sports.\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among them are five athletes beinghosted by the United KingdomNational Olympic Committee, who will compete in swimming, badminton, boxing, taekwondo and weightlifting.\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With more than 100 million people currently displaced around our world, the Refugee Olympic Team represents an important symbol of hope for those uprooted by conflict.\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999995401882336, \"rank\": 4.5981206997808623e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First introduced at the 2016Olympics, this will be the third time that a Refugee Olympic Team attends the games.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This year is also the biggest cohort that is heading to the Olympics, suggesting that our planet's refugee crisis is, unfortunately, growing.\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You will make billions of people around the world aware of the magnitude of the refugee crisis,\\\" said IOC President Thomas Bach.\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1210, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IOC President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1224, \"end\": 1235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Therefore, I encourage everyone, around the world, to join us in cheering for you - the IOC Refugee Olympic Team.\\\"\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"London named as 'the best food city in the world'  Bridgerton stars attend season four premiere in Paris  Mining merger talks see FTSE 100 end week on high  Winter escapes and activities to end the year in style  Here's everything you need to know about the Refugee Olympic Team and the vital role they play in representing refugees in sports.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1354, \"end\": 1360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2462283810747776e-17, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0258810452771647e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FTSE_100_Index\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FTSE 100\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FTSE_100_Index\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FTSE_100_Index\"}, {\"begin\": 1612, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999995401882336, \"rank\": 4.5981206997808623e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Refugee Olympic Team is a multi-national team of athletes who are also refugees.\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1703, \"end\": 1723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999995401882336, \"rank\": 4.5981206997808623e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team allows people who have fled their homes to still compete in the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than competing for a country, they compete under the flag of the Refugee Olympic Team and represent millions of people displaced from their homes worldwide.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1946, \"end\": 1966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999995401882336, \"rank\": 4.5981206997808623e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In previous years, the Refugee Olympic Team has featured some prominent sporting figures, including the Syrian swimmer Yusra Mardini, who later had a film made about her life called The Swimmers.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2062, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999995401882336, \"rank\": 4.5981206997808623e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2143, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrians\", \"score\": 0.9825232836078451, \"rank\": 0.01762985048696557, \"text\": \"Syrian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrians\"}, {\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusra_Mardini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yusra Mardini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusra_Mardini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusra_Mardini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcement of this year's team comes as countless conflicts continue to create refugees around our world.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Refugee Olympic Team is part of a wider initiative by the Olympic Refuge Foundation (ORF) that helps fund scholarships for athletes who are refugees.\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2353, \"end\": 2373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999995401882336, \"rank\": 4.5981206997808623e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2411, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Refuge_Foundation\", \"score\": 0.9999999957226464, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic Refuge Foundation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Refuge_Foundation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Refuge_Foundation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the years, the foundation has supported elite athletes while also unlocking access to sports for displaced people worldwide.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are 36 athletes from 11 countries that will form this year's Refugee Olympic Team.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2701, \"end\": 2721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999995401882336, \"rank\": 4.5981206997808623e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes originally come from Afghanistan, Cameroon, Congo, Cuba, Eritrea, Ethiopia, Iran, South Sudan, Sudan, Syria, and Venezuela.\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2758, \"end\": 2769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.212015441145596e-17, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 2771, \"end\": 2779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon\", \"score\": 0.9999998603348201, \"rank\": 1.3937197912319445e-07, \"text\": \"Cameroon\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon\"}, {\"begin\": 2781, \"end\": 2786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Democratic_Republic_of_the_Congo\", \"score\": 0.9999793291489415, \"rank\": 2.067043261407104e-05, \"text\": \"Congo\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Democratic_Republic_of_the_Congo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Democratic_Republic_of_the_Congo\"}, {\"begin\": 2788, \"end\": 2792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0572513456109267e-14, \"text\": \"Cuba\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"h