s\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3445, \"end\": 3451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rwanda\", \"score\": 0.9999999998976818, \"rank\": 1.0054924097552228e-10, \"text\": \"Rwanda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rwanda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rwanda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alongside the five stars hosted by the UK, the remaining 31 athletes are:  \\u2022 Farida Abaroge, athletics (1500m)  \\u2022 Omid Ahmadisafa, boxing (-51kg)  \\u2022 Yahya Al Ghotany, taekwondo (-68kg)  \\u2022 Mohammad Amin Alsalami, athletics (long jump)  \\u2022 Amir Ansari, cycling (time trial)  \\u2022 Sibghatullah Arab, judo (mixed team & -81kg)  \\u2022 Mahboubeh Barbari Zharfi, judo (mixed team & +78kg)  \\u2022 Edilio Francisco Centeno Nieves, shooting (10m air pistol)  \\u2022 Muna Dahouk, judo (mixed team & -57kg)  \\u2022 Jamal Abdelmaji Eisa Mohammed, athletics (10,000m)  \\u2022 Saeid Fazloula, canoe (K-1 1,000m)  \\u2022 Tachlowini Gabriyesos, athletics (marathon)  \\u2022 Eyeru Gebru, cycling (road race)  \\u2022 Yekta Jamali Galeh, weightlifting (-81kg)  \\u2022 Fernando Dayan Jorge Enriquez, canoe (C-1 1,000m)  \\u2022 Dorian Keletela, athletics (100m)  \\u2022 Adnan Khankan, judo (mixed team & -100kg)  \\u2022 Perina Lokure, athletics (800m)  \\u2022 Iman Mahdavi, wrestling (freestyle -74kg)  \\u2022 Alaa Maso, swimming (50m freestyle)  \\u2022 Kasra Mehdipournejad, taekwondo (+80kg)  \\u2022 Dina Pouryounes Langeroudi, taekwondo (-49kg)  \\u2022 Mohammad Rashnonezhad, judo (mixed team & -60kg)  \\u2022 Amir Rezanejad, canoe (canoe slalom)  \\u2022 Nigara Shaheen, judo (mixed team & -63kg)  \\u2022 Luna Solomon, shooting (10m air rifle)  \\u2022 Saman Soltani, canoe (K-1 500m)  \\u2022 Musa Suliman, athletics (800m)  \\u2022 Manizha Talash, breaking (Bgirl)  \\u2022 Hadi Tiranvalipour, taekwondo (